name: Lucy Perry
description:
I am very outgoing, and I love most activities outdoors. I am cute, & I would also like to say, I am Single,I am somewhat conservative, but am adventurous and love doing things from relax, listen to wide-range of music, watch good films, to taking walks along the beach or curling up in front of a fire with that special someone. I’m a down to earth real open-minded,I don’t hide my feelings when it comes to the matters of the heart. I want to share my life with someone who will love me for what I am and want the same in return. I am very happy with who I am as a Person, and I want to share & experience Life with a man who can share, and enjoy Companionship, and what I have, and who will treasure my Heart. I have good a Heart and I’m caring. "I am looking for someone who will Love me for whom I am".Honesty,
friendship, giving
